3. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) - The paper deals with graph drawing problems, which are inherently related to discrete mathematics. 
4. cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) - The paper discusses the problem of finding a planar drawing of a graph with prescribed vertex positions and y-monotone edges, which can be seen as a game between the vertices and the edges.
